    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0

    tmp = ((0.45 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.85)) + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.18) + tmp))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.62 + tmp + 0.23) / (tmp + 0.03 / v2 + 0.82)))
